      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nIf we go with 2-level hash, DNE does not need these hash codes from ldiskfs. But I thought this is still being discussed. \n\nEven we will use those ldiskfs hash, we probably should just copy these hash code into lmv module during build to avoid the dependency of ldiskfs. So these codes should be removed anyway, IMHO.",
